He’d stepped right into an ambush and spent the whole fight knocked out while his friends fended for themselves.
A son of Mercury … Jason felt like he should know that kid, but the name was missing from his mind.
“There are others like me.
You’ve got us.
I was having a dream…”He told them what he’d seen, and what the goddess had said inside her cage.
